findings.suggestion:
Current code is acceptable per project conventions. If this grows beyond 3 fields, consider:

const OPTIONAL_ARRAY_FIELDS = ['allowedTools', 'dependencies', 'tags'] as const
for (const field of OPTIONAL_ARRAY_FIELDS) {
  if (Array.isArray(parsed.data[field])) {
    (metadata as any)[field] = parsed.data[field]
  }
}

WHY: Only recommended if more optional array fields are added. The explicit version is currently more readable and type-safe.

