AFTER (add a factory helper at the top of the describe block):
  function createRegistry(): SkillRegistry {
    return new SkillRegistry({
      builtinSkillsDir: tmpBuiltin,
      userSkillsDir: tmpUser,
    })
  }

  // Then in each test:
